Watch on youtube: https://youtu.be/IXlrUWSz_xY Tags: 3dprint , material test , bambulab , nylon , ppacf , PPA-CF, the premium carbon fiber reinforced nylon by Bambu Lab is the strongest filament I tested so far (but not in every test). It requires a serious drying, but after this it is very printable filament. It needs a hardened steel nozzle and enclosure. Product page (affiliate link): https://shrsl.com/4pwr0 Forgot to mention in the video: This spool don't have RFID Tag, so drying in microwave is worth to try.
